bwwExcerpt: "Wonderland" has always had a talented cast and several solid songs and some good segments. But early on, parts of this play where stronger than the whole. Now it has come together into a fantasy adventure that could have a future on Broadway where it already has been playing in previews at the Marquis Theatre.
